<h1>A small appliance for difficult SIP networks.</h1>
<p class="lede">The VoiceTel SDN appliance sits inside the customer LAN and establishes a secure tunnel to VoiceTel, helping PBX registrations and media flows avoid common NAT, ALG, UDP timer, and firewall problems.</p>
